title: Metallica - Rare Tracks & Covers | MP3 320 | 1982-2016
description:

02. 53rd & 3rd (Ramones cover) [00:02:21] - from We're a happy family (2003)
03. Remember tomorrow (Iron Maiden cover) [00:05:46] - from Maiden heaven (2008)
04. You really got me (feat. Ray Davies) (The Kinks cover) [00:02:15] - from Ray Davies: See my friends (2010)
05. When a blind man cries (Deep Purple cover) [00:04:37] - from Re-Machined: A tribute to Deep Purple's Machine head (2012)
06. Ronnie rising medley (Rainbow cover) [00:09:04] - from Ronnie James Dio - This is your life (2014). Ronnie rising medley contains A Light In The Black, Tarot Woman, Stargazer, Kill The King
